    <entry>
      <title>Dart语法</title>
      <link href="/2019/01/01/flutter/001-flutter.dart-yu-fa/"/>
      <url>/2019/01/01/flutter/001-flutter.dart-yu-fa/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>Dart，谷歌开发，是面向对象的、类定义的、单继承的计算机编程语言，语法类似C语言，被用于Web、服务器、移动应用和互联网等领域。<span id="more"></span></p><h2 id="01、变量"><a href="#01、变量" class="headerlink" title="01、变量"></a>01、变量</h2><ul><li>新建一个MethodDefDemo.dart文件，代码如下。</li></ul><pre class="line-numbers language-dart"><code class="language-dart"><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">/* 有返回值的main()方法main() {  print("你好，Dart！");} */</span><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">// 没有返回值的main()方法</span><span class="token keyword">void</span> <span class="token function">main</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token punctuation">{</span>  <span class="token function">print</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token string">"你好，Dart！"</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span><span class="token punctuation">}</span><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">//  注释方法一</span><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">/// 注释方法二</span><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">/*  注释方法三  */</span><span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><ul><li>新建一个DefVariableDemo.dart文件，代码如下。</li></ul><pre class="line-numbers language-dart"><code class="language-dart"><span class="token function">main</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token punctuation">{</span>  <span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">// 自动推断变量类型时使用var</span>  <span class="token keyword">var</span> str1 <span class="token operator">=</span> <span class="token string">"var关键词定义变量."</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>  <span class="token keyword">var</span> myNum1 <span class="token operator">=</span> <span class="token number">123456789</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>  <span class="token function">print</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>str1<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>  <span class="token function">print</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>myNum1<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>  <span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">// 变量类型不明确时使用dynamic</span>  <span class="token keyword">dynamic</span> name <span class="token operator">=</span> <span class="token string">"bsf"</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>  <span class="token function">print</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token string">"My name is $name."</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>  <span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">// 显式声明，指定变量类型</span>  String str2 <span class="token operator">=</span> <span class="token string">"指定字符串类型定义."</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>  int myNum2 <span class="token operator">=</span> <span class="token number">987654321</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>  <span class="token function">print</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>str2<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>  <span class="token function">print</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>myNum2<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>  <span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">// 变量区分大小写</span>  <span class="token keyword">var</span> age <span class="token operator">=</span> <span class="token number">26</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>  <span class="token keyword">var</span> Age <span class="token operator">=</span> <span class="token number">30</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>  <span class="token function">print</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token string">"age: $age"</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>  <span class="token function">print</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token string">"Age: $Age"</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span><span class="token punctuation">}</span><span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><ul><li>新建一个DefConstantDemo.dart文件，代码如下。</li></ul><pre class="line-numbers language-dart"><code class="language-dart"><span class="token function">main</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token punctuation">{</span>  <span class="token keyword">var</span> str <span class="token operator">=</span> <span class="token string">"这是变量."</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>  str <span class="token operator">=</span> <span class="token string">"变量可以修改."</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>  <span class="token function">print</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>str<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>  <span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">// 常量使用const定义，不可修改的变量</span>  <span class="token keyword">const</span> PI <span class="token operator">=</span> <span class="token number">3.14</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>  <span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">// 常量使用final定义，不可修改的变量</span>  <span class="token keyword">final</span> ASTRO <span class="token operator">=</span> <span class="token string">"moon"</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>  <span class="token function">print</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>PI<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>  <span class="token function">print</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>ASTRO<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>  <span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">// final关键词有const编译时常量的特性，是运行时常量</span>  <span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">// final也是惰性初始化，即运行时第一次使用前才初始化</span>  <span class="token keyword">final</span> time1 <span class="token operator">=</span> <span class="token keyword">new</span> <span class="token class-name">DateTime<span class="token punctuation">.</span>now</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>  <span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">// const time2 = new DateTime.now(); // 报错</span>  <span class="token function">print</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>time1<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span><span class="token punctuation">}</span><span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><h2 id="02、数据类型"><a href="#02、数据类型" class="headerlink" title="02、数据类型"></a>02、数据类型</h2><ul><li>新建一个DefConstantDemo.dart文件，代码如下。</li></ul><pre class="line-numbers language-dart"><code class="language-dart"><span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre><ul><li>新建一个DefConstantDemo.dart文件，代码如下。</li></ul><pre class="line-numbers language-dart"><code class="language-dart"><span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre><ul><li>新建一个DefConstantDemo.dart文件，代码如下。</li></ul><pre class="line-numbers language-dart"><code class="language-dart"><span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre><ul><li>新建一个DefConstantDemo.dart文件，代码如下。</li></ul><pre class="line-numbers language-dart"><code class="language-dart"><span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre>]]></content>
      
      
